  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective randomized double-blind study on the effect of prebiotics (inulin and
      fructo-oligosaccharides) in the prevention of antibiotic-associated diarrhea in children.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Group will get either the product or placebo blindly throughout antibiotic treatment with
      additional 14 days.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
